| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3448 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ecf51d71-ca20-5a66-9e90-c563dbca77d1"
